ygData.subject: Re: gnome necro in Neriak?
ygData.msgSnippet: Excuse me? I am a gnome and my god is innorukk. I have been to the dark elf city before, and am tolerated on the upper leves but cant go to the lower yet,
ygData.messageBody:
Excuse me? I am a gnome and my god is innorukk. I have been to the dark elf
city before, and am tolerated on the upper leves but cant go to the lower
yet, still killing halflings.

-----Original Message-----
